{"tid":2184701,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"三個小問題，如果有人答到我就好啦","createTime":"2020-09-01T17:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T10:39:23.000Z","uid":363482,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0d1f6a7aca63b3411c99cd8223b8a78062ed5338","tid":2184701,"uid":363482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T17:52:59.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"right\"><br />\n1. 香港系乜嘢地方<br />\n2. 香港點來ga<br />\n3. 香港未來會點<br />\n<br />\n我自己答下自己ge意見先<br />\n<br />\n香港系特別行政區，行兩制，<br />\n香港系根據基本法，行三分。<br />\n<br />\n香港系由小海港發展成大城市，當中源于22年前一句不變。<br />\n堅定擁護過去中華人民共和國領導人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></p><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"left\">堅定擁護中華人民共和國領導人<br />\n左靠下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</p><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"right\">香港未來一片光明，黨中央領導下堅定不移，沒有三分，做乜都得。<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20200526/hong-kong-china/zh-hant/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.nytimes.com%2Fchina%2F20200526%2Fhong-kong-china%2Fzh-hant%2F&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYVGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=236ab02c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20200526/hong-kong-china/zh-hant/</a></p><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"left\"><br />\n包底保護下自己先<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以上言論為支持港安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</p><br />\n<p class=\"right\">你地左右又點分？</p>"},{"pid":"d57cccf5a4ec61e4c5a4742b4800c50a89914227","tid":2184701,"uid":263256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T10:39:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}